headline.print_headline: Norovirus Sickens 200 People on New Zealand Cruise
headline.main: Norovirus Sickens 200 People on New Zealand Cruise

lead_paragraph: Health authorities in New Zealand said Monday that about 200 passengers on a cruise ship have been sickened by an outbreak of norovirus.
